Eliya to ldoinyo le Sinai


1  Neliki Ahab Yesebel nena pooki naataasa Eliya. Oina sii natara metuata iloibonok pooki to lalem. 
2  Neitoki Yesebel airriwaki Eliya olkilikuai, ejo, “Maaitaasa nanu nkaitin ina, naaitulus sii, teneitu nanu aitotiu enkishui ino anaa enkishui e obo lenye tena saa taisere.” 
3  Neureishoyu ninye neinyototo aisik, nelo Beer-sheba e Yuda neing'uaa osinka lenye teine. 
4   Kake ore ninye makewan eshomo elototo enkolong nabo tiong'ota. Nelo aton te ntonata olchani oata oloip. Neomonu pee eye, ejo, “Eiririkine Olaitoriani, iwuang'ie enkishui ai, amu maikash nanu too loo papa.”


5  Neirrag ninye airura to loip lo lchani, naa ng'ura neiseyie olmalaika ninye nejoki ninye, “Tudumunye inosa endaa.” 
6  Neing'orisho ninye, naa ng'ura etii embata e ndukuya enye emukate natapejoki too soito ooirowua, o esiang'au e nkare. Nedaa ninye neokisho, neitoki airrag. 
7  Neitoki olmalaika lo Laitoriani enkata e are, neiseyie ninye, nejoki, “Tudumunye inosa endaa, amu kegolu elototo te iyie.” 
8  Nedumunye ninye nedaa neokisho, nelo te ngolon eina daa nainosa too nkolong'i artam, o nkewarietin artam, omeshomo Horeb ilo doinyo le Nkai. 
9  Nebau ninye enkapune neirrag ine, naa ng'ura, eewuo ororei lo Laitoriani enetii ninye, nejoki ninye, “Kaa iasita tene, Eliya?”


10   Nejo ninye, “Aata apa nanu olom to Laitoriani, Enkai oo lororani, amu etanyaita iltung'ana loo Siraeli olning'o lino, nesulaa ilpereren loo lasarri, near iloibonok linono metuata to lalem; metaa nanu ake, nanu ake openy otelekua; neing'oru ninche enkishui ai, pee eiwuang'ie.”


11  Neitoki ajoki, “Shomo ntasho te nchumata o ldoinyo te dukuya Olaitoriani.” Naa ng'ura eloito Olaitoriani agiroo, nekut olkutati kitok ogol lelo doinyo, nebel ndapidapo aitaa mbelibelat te dukuya Olaitoriani, kake metii Olaitoriani atua olkutati. Ore te siadi olkutati nelotu enkikirikirata enkop, kake metii Olaitoriani atua enkikirikirata e Nkop.


12  Ore te siadi enkikirikirata enkop nelotu enkima, kake metii Olaitoriani atua enkima. Ore te siadi enkima nelotu oloti toilo obor. 
13  Ore ake pee ening Eliya ina, neimulumul enkomom enye to lkila nelo aitashe te nkutuk e nkapune. Naa ng'ura nelotu oltoilo enetii ninye, nejoki, “Kaa iyie iasita tene, Eliya?”


14  Nejo ninye, “Aata apa nanu olom te nkaraki Olaitoriani Enkai oo lororani amu etanyaita iltung'ana loo Siraeli olning'o lino, neuroo ilpereren linono loo lasarri, near iloibonok linono metuata tolalem, netaa nanu ake openy otelekua, neing'oru ninche enkishui ai peyie eiwuang'ie.”


15   Nejoki Olaitoriani ninye, “Torrinyoyu shomo te nkoitoi ino enkalo e ong'ata e Dameski; ore ake pee ibaya, nilo abukoki eilata Hasael, aput metaa olaiguanani le Siria. 
16   Niput Yehu olayioni le Nimshi metaa olaiguanani loo Siraeli. Ore Elisha olayioni le Shefat le Abel-mehola, nibukoki eilata aput metaa oloiboni le Nkai te rishata ino. 
17  Ore ilo oilanya olalem le Hasael nelo Yehu aar metua. Ore ilo oilany olalem le Yehu nelo Elisha aar metua. 
18   Ore ake eyia kaleku nanu nkalifuni naapishana tiatua Isiraeli, lelo pooki leitu egilaki kung neitu eirrugokino Baal, o pooki leitu eng'utut Baal.”

Enkipototo e Elisha


19  Kaae nelo Eliya teine, nelo atum Elisha olayioni le Shefat eturishore ilmong'i tomon oare. Netii apa ninye tenebo ilo kiteng le tomon oare. Negiroo Eliya ninye nenang'aki olkila lenye. 
20  Neing'ua Elisha lelo mong'i nekuet asujaa Eliya, nejoki ninye, “Nchooki nanu mashomo ang'utut papaai o yieyioo aisho ole sere, pee aatum atusuja iyie.”

Nejoki Eliya ninye, “Torrinyoyu shomo; amu kaa nanu aaitaasa iyie?” 
21  Nerrinyo ninye te sujata enye, neitayu nena keek oo murto oo lmong'i neyieng ninche. Neyier nkiri enye tenebo nkeek oo murto oo lmong'i. Neisho iltung'ana meinosa, neinos ninche. Neitoki ninye adumunye alo asujaa Eliya nelo aisiaai ninye.

